FIG. 4 is a graph showing doping effects for the exemplary transparent CNT electrodes produced in Example 3 according to the concentration of dopant solutions and doping time; and
FIG. 5 is a graph showing doping effects for the exemplary transparent CNT electrodes produced in Example 4 with varying light transmittance values of the transparent CNT electrodes.
